metadata.name: Time
metadata.description:
INPUT: 

"Write a prompt for midjourney that creates a surreal painting that incorporates the following lyrics by pink floyd: “ You are young and life is long and there is time to kill today. And then one day you find ten years have got behind you. No one told you when to run, you missed the starting gun”

OUTPUT:

"Visualize the abstract concept of time as a flowing river, with a young person at the beginning of their journey, unaware of the relentless current carrying them forward. In the distance, an older version of the same person stands on a crumbling bridge, with a decade of memories and experiences fading into the mist. They appear bewildered, holding an hourglass that has run out of sand.

In the background, a starting gun lays abandoned on the shore, half-submerged in the water, and overgrown with vines. The sky above the scene displays a cosmic dance of planets, stars, and galaxies, symbolizing the vastness of the universe and the insignificance of human perception of time."
